definition:
A man of the tribe of Gad living at the time of Egypt and Wilderness, first mentioned at Gen.46.16; 
 son of: Gad (H1410); 
 brother of: Ziphion (H6837), Haggi (H2291), Shuni (H7764), Ezbon (H0675), Eri (H6179) and Arod (H0720) 
 § Areli = "lion of God"
1) a son of Gad
2) those of the family of Areli (pater adj-Arelites)
